         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="96.34.2_0011"/><date>22. X. 917</date></dateline><salute>Verehrter Herr Doktor,</salute></opener><p>wollen Sie mir am <date>Donner<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date> gegen <time>7 Uhr</time> das Vergnügen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chenken<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o möcht ich Ihnen gern mancher<unclear>lei</unclear> über Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr
               intere<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>antes <rs type="work" ref="#pmb33608" subtype="implied"><hi rend="latintype">Manuscript</hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agen.</p><closer>mit herzl Gruß Ihr erg<lb/><signed>Arth Schn</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
